snippet.title: Prism Land (PSX, 2000)
snippet.description:
Help Prim the Cat and his friend Princess Rythm save Queen Rilis from unthinkable evil that threatens Prism Land in the only way they know how; by playing Arkanoid! Known as Prism Land Story in Japan and Sorcerer's Maze in USA.



Get it here: https://retro.gg/game/prism-land/540/
